00:01:53.345 --> 00:01:56.081 align:start size:97% position:3%
as the symptoms, and then they
want a sprayer or something

00:01:56.081 --> 00:01:58.351 align:start size:97% position:3%
to kill what's above ground
and we're focused on promoting

00:01:58.351 --> 00:02:03.222
