00:07:32.952 --> 00:07:36.622 align:start size:97% position:3%
As soon as they take a
bite, it just sends a signal

00:07:36.622 --> 00:07:39.624 align:start size:97% position:3%
to their brain, like,
okay, this is what we want.

00:07:39.624 --> 00:07:41.460
- [Narrator] Sending
yearly goats to market

00:07:41.460 --> 00:07:45.330
