00:07:59.611 --> 00:08:00.679
- [Greg] They gain great on it.

00:08:00.679 --> 00:08:01.948
- [Carolina] Oh,
yeah, they gain.

00:08:01.948 --> 00:08:03.148
- [Greg] Yeah!

00:08:03.148 --> 00:08:04.483 align:start size:84% position:16%
- [Carolina] But
it's a high protein.

00:08:04.483 --> 00:08:06.185
- They do well on spurge.

00:08:06.185 --> 00:08:07.887
- 20% protein or something.

00:08:09.254 --> 00:08:13.025 align:start size:97% position:3%
- [Narrator] And these animals
are incredibly adaptable.

00:08:13.025 --> 00:08:16.762 align:start size:97% position:3%
- [Carolina] We like a Spanish
goat with lots of cashmere

00:08:16.762 --> 00:08:19.965 align:start size:97% position:3%
